<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Steven </PERSON> <PERSON> Komarow </PERSON> is a Washington-based reporter for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> who is covering Sen. <PERSON> Lloyd </PERSON> <PERSON> Bentsen </PERSON>'s campaign
