ORGANIZATION> World </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Bank </ORGANIZATION> lent <LOCATION> Burundi </LOCATION> 153.5 million dollars during fiscal 1988 for projects promoting agriculture, rural development, health, nutrition, education, small business and birth control.
